data.description: CUSTOM HOME! This property is in a desirable location and located just 15 minutes North of Hayden! 1672 sq ft home with an attached 2-car garage and 30x40 shop, 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a desirable split bedroom floor plan. The spacious living room opens to the dining area and kitchen featuring which features a large double island and pantry. The master suite offers a walk-in closet and private bathroom with a walk-in shower and separate soaker tub. All on 6.23 acres of treed flat usable land.
